reviewText: I didn't make it through the first five minutes...so annoying. Not my kind of movie at all.
Great movie. Webb was incredible. But disc would not pls all the way through. I tried several players.

Got to see this for the premiere and I really enjoyed it. It's a powerful film that really grabs you from the beginning and really pushes your imagination to the limits. The director, Brandon, really brought a great vision to the big screen, and he really does a great job in capturing a unique and engrossing story. I highly recommend this film to anyone who likes a touch of Sci-Fi with a big thrill ride of a film all the way till the end.
